BSalt
=====

A theoretical student and curriculum management system for IF battle school.

Purposes:
Commandants:
-- Track potential recruits (all chilren on earth under age 8)
-- Track student progress
-- Read student messages
-- send messages as students
Teachers:
-- give assignments/marks
-- send/read messages
Students
-- View own progress, assignments, marks.
-- send/read messages


- interface for tracking likely students 
    (that is, every child on earth under age...8?)
-- age
-- competativeness
-- agression
-- creativity
-- memory
-- nationality
-- notes
-- birthplace
-- name
-- parents/guardian names
- tracking current students the above, plus:
-- conflicts
-- platoon membership
---- through rank
-- progress in videogame
-- marks in classes
-- rankings in game
---- accuracy
---- kills
---- deaths/disable
-- 

For student:
-- display relative to classmates

Platoons
-- Rank
-- members
